  <description>
    <p>
      KeySmith provides a user-friendly graphical interface for managing SSH keys.
      It simplifies the process of generating new key pairs, viewing existing keys,
      copying public keys, and deploying them to servers.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Generate new Ed25519 SSH key pairs.</li>
      <li>List keys from ~/.ssh with their type and fingerprint.</li>
      <li>Easily copy public keys for services like GitHub or GitLab.</li>
      <li>Deploy public keys to servers using ssh-copy-id.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

